<title>SRI LANKA: Weather-Thunder storms seen over Sri Lanka.</title>
<headline>Weather-Thunder storms seen over Sri Lanka.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sri Lanka's meteorological department released the following rainfall figures for 24 hours ending Tuesday morning</p>
<p>Hydro catchment areas (in mm):</p>
<p>    Bowathenna		  0</p>
<p>    Canyon			0</p>
<p>    Castlereigh		 0</p>
<p>    Kotmale		     2.0</p>
<p>    Laxapana		    0</p>
<p>    Moussakele		  0</p>
<p>    Norton			0</p>
<p>    Polgolla		    0</p>
<p>    Randenigala		 2.2</p>
<p>    Victoria		    7.5</p>
<p>    Samanalawewa		5.2</p>
<p>    Ukuwela		     0</p>
<p>    Rantembe		    0</p>
<p>The department forecast thundershowers at a few places over the island during the afternoon and evening on Wednesday.</p>
